data.name: LineProperties
desc: This is a set of properties to describe the style for rendering a Line.
The properties for line ends and line starts are only supported by shapes with open line ends.

properties.name: LineCap
desc: This property defines the rendering of ends of thick lines.

properties.name: LineColor
desc: This property contains the line color.

properties.name: LineDash
desc: This property contains the dash of the line.

properties.name: LineDashName
desc: This property contains the name of the dash of the line.

properties.name: LineEnd
desc: This property contains the line end in the form of a poly polygon Bezier.

properties.name: LineEndCenter
desc: If this property is TRUE, the line will end in the center of the polygon.

properties.name: LineEndName
desc: This property contains the name of the line end poly polygon Bezier.
If this string is empty, no line end polygon is rendered.

properties.name: LineEndWidth
desc: This property contains the width of the line end polygon.

properties.name: LineJoint
desc: This property defines the rendering of joints between thick lines.

properties.name: LineStart
desc: This property contains the line start in the form of a poly polygon Bezier.

properties.name: LineStartCenter
desc: If this property is TRUE, the line will start from the center of the polygon.

properties.name: LineStartName
desc: This property contains the name of the line start poly polygon Bezier.
If this string is empty, no line start polygon is rendered.

properties.name: LineStartWidth
desc: This property contains the width of the line start polygon.

properties.name: LineStyle
desc: This property contains the type of the line.

properties.name: LineTransparence
desc: This property contains the extent of transparency.

properties.name: LineWidth
desc: This property contains the width of the line in 1/100th mm.
